metadata.name: Satomaa #1
metadata.description:
Introducing Satomma, one of the 22 Budweiser Royalty artists. This Hip Hop and Alternative Tracks musician is from Litchfield Park, AZ and has 500 NFTs available, allowing early fans to proudly represent her.

Core NFTs act as collectibles, letting holders show off that they were fans since the beginning. Rare and Ultra Rare NFTs will unlock levels of access and offer a chance for a closer relationship with your artist. This project and rewards are only obtainable by 21+ (or legal drinking age) NFT collectors. Terms and Conditions apply.
